I use Emacs.

http://vh213601.truman.edu/~belanger

* ComicsMode is a program that will allow you to download and view comics (such as Dilbert and User Friendly).
* QuotesMode allows you to browse and search through a collection of quotes.
* GradeMode is a program to keep track of (and compute) students' grades.
* BalanceMode is what I use to keep track of my checking account.
* GoobookMode provides an interface to goobook.

